参考答案：¶

The outgoing longwave: 240.26691846331997 W/m2¶

The outgoing shortwave: 99.13806041149408 W/m2¶

The TOA incoming solar: 340.28326598091286 W/m2¶

The outgoing longwave + The outgoing shortwave = The TOA net incoming solar¶
